commit.title: [ci] [azure] Rework windows Azure pipeline
commit.message:
[ci] [azure] Rework windows Azure pipeline

- use a different mirror for main cygwin archive
- (always) publish build log as artifact
- fix call to dune makefiles
- we do test & build of Azure win in one step, as dune is rebuilding
  Coq to run the test-suite, this needs move investigation.
